{"tid":2508648,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"須藤早貴亡夫喪禮片段曝光 未亡人玩手機露出勝利笑容","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T02:18:39.000Z","uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b237fab3cf60e025c8ce43e40af21a654fca6d3","tid":2508648,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LWWw3q-AH5GmLjQM4FSbmpLniZo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4SRALOZINH45NGQJ2EMMFLMYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLWWw3q-AH5GmLjQM4FSbmpLniZo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4SRALOZINH45NGQJ2EMMFLMYQ.jpg&h=3858a1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n77歲日本富商野崎幸助，在2018年5月24日於家中暴斃，警方認定野崎是服用過量興奮劑致死，野崎的25歲嫩妻須藤早貴今日被警方以涉嫌謀殺被拘捕。曾以假名拍下五套AV的須藤早貴，被日媒再揭真面目，公開她參加丈夫喪禮當日的絕密片段，見她毫無悲傷之情，反而笑得相當燦爛，令人毛骨悚然。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210428/YBOQMFVSNFHWDKCPTFJTLOJ44U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210428%2FYBOQMFVSNFHWDKCPTFJTLOJ44U%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzYjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=fc47bd0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210428%2FYBOQMFVSNFHWDKCPTFJTLOJ44U%2F&h=1e4dcb8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210428/YBOQMFVSNFHWDKCPTFJTLOJ44U/</a>"}]}